Gas Town provides the core engine (rigs, polecats, beads, merge queue,
Dolt integration, tmux orchestration, session management, the gt CLI
framework, and the underlying role architecture). Camp Leatherneck adds
a Marine-themed persona overlay, standing roles (Fire Watch, RTO), the
Self-Correction Loop doctrine, Diagnostic Discipline rules, a Sitrep
generator, and an installable distribution.

